cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with a deep learning architecture for obstacle detection in the context of autonomous driving. This falls under the intersection of computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the use of limited data and proposes a multi-stage training procedure, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with the design of the neural network architecture, which is a topic in neural networks (cs.NE).
